{
    "manually_checked": false,
    "poem_title": "Las violetas",
    "author": "Julio Valdelomar Fábregas",
    "poem_alt_title": "Ocultas en festones de ventura,",
    "corpus": "disco2_1",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": "1",
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "1",
                    "line_text": "Ocultas en festones de ventura,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "2",
                    "line_text": "son el símbolo fiel del alma buena,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+--+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "3",
                    "line_text": "que es al bullicio mundanal ajena,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "4",
                    "line_text": "y que busca en la fe su fuente pura.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ocultas en festones de ventura,\nson el símbolo fiel del alma buena,\nque es al bullicio mundanal ajena,\ny que busca en la fe su fuente pura."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "2",
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "5",
                    "line_text": "Unen a la modestia la hermosura,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+----+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "6",
                    "line_text": "y si los cierzos le procuran pena,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "7",
                    "line_text": "ellas doblan su cáliz, en la arena,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "8",
                    "line_text": "buscando, con temor, la sombra oscura.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Unen a la modestia la hermosura,\ny si los cierzos le procuran pena,\nellas doblan su cáliz, en la arena,\nbuscando, con temor, la sombra oscura."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "3",
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "9",
                    "line_text": "Flores hermosas, si el placer convida",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "10",
                    "line_text": "con el afán creciente y el anhelo,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "11",
                    "line_text": "que dejan luego el alma dolorida,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Flores hermosas, si el placer convida\ncon el afán creciente y el anhelo,\nque dejan luego el alma dolorida,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "4",
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "12",
                    "line_text": "yo, en cambio, busco mi mayor consuelo",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "13",
                    "line_text": "en recordar la madre de mi vida,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "14",
                    "line_text": "y en vuestro suave aroma que es del cielo.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "yo, en cambio, busco mi mayor consuelo\nen recordar la madre de mi vida,\ny en vuestro suave aroma que es del cielo."
        }
    ]
}